title: 753. Reaction to Rams vs. Cardinals Game & Importance of Strength at WR
itunes:title: 753. Reaction to Rams vs. Cardinals Game & Importance of Strength at WR
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys react to the Los Angeles Rams vs. Arizona Cardinals Monday Night Football game. After that, the duo look at the importance of depth on rosters, especially in today's NFL with increased positive COVID cases and a longer season. To wrap up the show, the pair emphasize how crucial strength is in wide receivers, while also focusing on the league's top wide receivers.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
